            <h2>
                    鬼吹灯Ⅱ之一·黄皮子坟的书评 · · · · · ·

                    <span class="pl">( <a href="reviews">全部 36 条</a> )</span>
            </h2>
        </header>
        
            
            <div class="review_filter">
                            <a href="javascript:;;" class="cur" data-sort="">热门</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="time">最新</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="follow">好友</a>
                        <a href="/subject/2149655/reviews?version=1" data-sort="version">只看本版本的评论</a>
            </div>
            <script>
                var cur_sort = '';
                $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').on('click', function () {
                    var sort = $(this).data('sort');
                    if(sort === cur_sort) return;

                    if(sort === 'follow' && true){
                        window.location.href = '//www.douban.com/accounts/login?source=movie';
                        return;
                    }

                    if($('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing')) return;
                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', true);

                    cur_sort = sort;

                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').removeClass('cur');
                    $(this).addClass('cur');

                    $.getJSON('reviews', { sort: sort }, function(res) {
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper [href="reviews?sort=follow"]').parent().remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').after(res.html);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', false);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').removeData('doing');

                        if (res.count === 0) {
                            $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').html('<span class="no-review">你关注的人还没写过长评</span>');
                        }
                    });
                });
            </script>


            



<div class="review-list  ">
        
    

            
    
    <div data-cid="12109977">
        <div class="main review-item" id="12109977">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qingxinxxx/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u189059562-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qingxinxxx/" class="name">清悠居士</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2019-12-20" class="main-meta">2019-12-20 11:29:09</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/26692166/">青岛出版社2016版</a>
            </span>
    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/12109977/">鬼吹灯黄皮子坟——青春时代赞歌</a></h2>

                <div id="review_12109977_short" class="review-short" data-rid="12109977">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇书评可能有关键情节透露</p>

                        黄皮子坟这本书从故事情节还是写作文笔上，很明显是两个故事组成的。第一个是大兴安岭的黄皮子坟探秘，第二个是草原上的百眼窟小鬼子研究基地冒险。这本书也是一贯的天下霸唱风格，虎头蛇尾开头的黄皮子坟写的十分精彩，尤其是东北的民风让读者印象深刻，仿佛回到了文革时期的...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-12109977-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_12109977_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_12109977_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

